# Static export build output — regenerated on every build.
# Deployed via `wrangler pages deploy out/` straight from build artifacts;
# tracking this churns 2500 files per commit and bloats PR diffs.
out/
# Cloudflare Wrangler temp files — ephemeral per deploy.
.wrangler/
# iCloud creates numbered-suffix copies during sync conflicts
# (e.g. ".next 2", "out 3"). They can contain webpack cache .pack files
# that exceed GitHub's 100MB per-file limit and block the push.
*\ 2
*\ 3
*\ 4
